it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.ip4

Class Ip4AddressPrefix

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.ip4.Ip4Address
      • it.unipr.netsec.ipstack.ip4.Ip4AddressPrefix
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IpAddress, IpAddressPrefix, Address

    public class Ip4AddressPrefix
extends Ip4Address
implements IpAddressPrefix
    Internet Protocol version 4 (IPv4) address with prefix length.

    It extends class Ip4Address by simply adding prefix length information.
